original_article.title: Bitcoin price eyes $116K liquidity sweep with ETF comeback in focus
original_article.summary: William Suberg 5 minutes ago Bitcoin price eyes $116K liquidity sweep with ETF comeback in focus Bitcoin ETF netflows may be key in gauging market appetite as exchange order-book liquidity puts $116,000 top of the list for bulls. Listen 0:00 40 Market Update COINTELEGRAPH IN YOUR SOCIAL FEEDKey points:Bitcoin bounces as liquidation guardrails appear above and below price, making $116,000 a key level to watch. Expectations call for BTC price support to hold above $110,000 should bears take control.
